episodes.title: TWIN FLAMES CULT & Life Coach Grifters -Tristan Haggard & Jay Dyer
episodes.description: Jay Dyer and Tristan (Twin Flames?) explore the millennial new-ager normie cult phenomenon of "Twin Flame" relationship gurus and the nihilistic pop-culture of narcissism, self-love, isolation, and desperate search for meaning and truth that breeds these strange post-Christian cults. A fun comedic deep dive on the world of Twin Flames, including analysis of the Netflix doc series "Escaping Twin Flames" and the Amazon Prime documentary "Desperately Seeking Soulmate: Escaping Twin Flames Universe" Tristan is here: https://www.youtube.com/@tristanhaggardPurchase our books here: https://jaysanalysis.com/shop/
